Miscellaneous Highlights: Washington Commanders quarterback Jayden Daniels was at the game and received a huge ovation from the crowd
Others: Golden State Warriors guard Stephen Curry scored 16 of his 24 points in the second half in his return from an ankle injury
Buddy Hield scored 20 points, part of another strong contribution from the Golden State bench
Jordan Poole led Washington with 24 points
Kyle Kuzma (right groin strain) missed his third straight game for the Wizards, and Marvin Bagley III (illness) also sat out
